          <h3 class="font-bold text-orange-900 mb-1">
            Key Requirement: The 9-Month Rule
          </h3>
          <p class="text-orange-800 text-sm">
            You must have been working full-time for your B.C. employer <strong
              >for at least 9 consecutive months</strong
            > before you can register. This work must be in the same job you are applying
            for.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2>Who is ELSS For?</h2>
        <p>ELSS is ideal if you:</p>
